Used to search for products, enterprises and branches

POST <http://{host}:{port}/search/:field>

**:field**: the name or test field of the wanted research

## Request body rules
~~~typescript
{
  "filters": Array<{ "key":String,"value":String }>, required //an array from the filters to your research
}
~~~
## Response structure
~~~typescript
{
  "result": Array<Enterprise|Branch|Product|undefined> // an array containing the result for your research
}
~~~

## Request example
POST <http://localhost:3333/search/feira> 

## Request body example
~~~json
{
  "filters": [
    {
      "key": "Local",
      "value": "Rua central"
    }
  ]
}
~~~
## Response example
~~~json
{
  [
    {
      "name": "passeio pela feira de penedo",
       ...rest
    }
  ]
}
~~~

